name: DOG
description: DOG is the next-generation decentralized crypto asset issued based on the X Layer public chain. It is not merely a token, but a financial ecosystem centered on community co-construction, automatic combustion, and dual dividends. DOG's goal is to create a benchmark for crypto assets with stable value growth and sustainable returns for holders. LP combustion mechanism LP burning is automatically executed every 12 hours. The total combustion volume is 0.25% of the liquidity pool. This mechanism ensures that the number of DOG tokens in the market gradually decreases, creating a combination of scarcity and stable upward momentum.
